<Link id="l00150" /><CodeLine lineNumber="150"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Create a new leaf block for the binary lookup tree. It checks if the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00151" /><CodeLine lineNumber="151"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// switch&#39;s value == the case&#39;s value. If not, then it jumps to the default</span></CodeLine>
